            <h2>Meet Malachi</h2>
            <h4>Born February 2000</h4>
            <p>Malachi is thinking about joining the U.S. Marines when he finishes high school. He went to a military boot camp and loved it and is very interested in working out, keeping his body fit. Physical education is his favorite class in school.</p>
<p>Here’s what Malachi says he would like in a family: Nice, loving parents that take care of him; a little brother or sister; a nice, safe area to live in; a family with rules but one that isn’t overbearing; and parents who will let him drive.</p>
<p>We love how he describes himself: “Caring, doesn’t give up on people easily, makes others smile…goal-oriented, able to apologize.”</p>
<p></p>
